title.en: Cinderella no Ane desu ga, Fuhoninagara Ouji to Kekkon suru Koto ni narimashita ~Migawari Outaishi-hi wa Rikyuu de Slow Life wo Mankitsu suru~
Gyakkou Saki ga (Moto) Konyakusha no Nakatte Dou Iu Koto desu ka? Konyaku Hakisareta no ni "Karada no Naka" de Dousei suru Koto ni Narimashita
Akuyaku Reijou wa Mou Zenbu ga Iya ni Natta no de, Kioku Soushitsu no Furi wo suru Koto ni shita
Watakushi no Koto ga Daikirai na Gitei ga Goei Kishi ni narimashita
Ryuuou-sama, Kono Kekkon wa Nakatta Koto ni shite kudasai!
Cinderella no Giri Ane ni Tensei shitakedo Futari no Ouji ni Dekiaisareteimasu
Kono Tabi Fuhoninagara, Kami-sama no Hanayome ni narimashita
Denka, Anata ga Suteta Onna ga Honmono no Seijo desu
Ai wo Shiranai Aigan Ningyou ni wa Hakoiri Reijou no Oteire ga Hitsuyou desu.
Yake wo Okoshita Koushaku Reijou wa Sugata wo Kuramashi Jiyuu wo Tanoshimu
Narikin Reijou no Shiawase na Kekkon - Kane no Mouja to Nonoshirareta Reijou wa Chichioya ni Urarete Henkyou no Buta Koushaku to Shiawase ni naru
Ouji, Konyaku Haki Shita no wa Sochira na no de, Kowai Kao de Kocchi Niramanaide kudasai.
Imouto ni Konyakusha wo Toraretara Mishiranu Koushaku-sama ni Kyuukonsaremashita
Imouto no Migawari de Totsuida Hazu ga, Douyara Watashi ga Shin no Seijo Datta you desu
Seijo no Ane desu ga, Naze ka Miwaku no Koushaku-sama ni Tsukaeru Koto ni narimashita
